OL,3,CAnimal charity's appeal to make life
OL,4,Cbetter for grieving cats like Penny
OL,6,FAn animal rescue centre has started a
OL,7,F#12,000 appeal to help make life
OL,8,Feasier for cats who have been rescued.
OL,10,FThe centre needs to upgrade the doors
OL,11,Fto the cattery which currently make
OL,12,Floud noises frightening the animals.
OL,14,FOne of the cats recently taken in by
OL,15,FBristol Animal Rescue Centre is Penny,
OL,16,Fwho was afraid and anxious to be in a
OL,17,Fnew environment after her owner passed
OL,18,Faway.
