OL,3,CAnimal charity's appeal to make life
OL,4,Cbetter for grieving cats like Penny
OL,6,FThe current cattery doors, installed
OL,7,Fin 1992, create sudden loud noises,
OL,8,Ffurther distressing cats like Penny.
OL,10,FBristol A.R.C. is hoping to install
OL,11,Fnew, quieter UPVC doors to alleviate
OL,12,Fstress and provide a more private
OL,13,Fsanctuary for its feline residents,
OL,14,Fespecially for those experiencing
OL,15,Fgrief and trauma.
